ARKANOID II:

        On the high score screen, type 'DEBBIE S' for unlimited lives.

        On the title screen type "WHENWORLDSCOLLIDE".  Now start the game
        and use 'S' to open the gate to the next level.

        On the title screen, type "ROBOCOPPER" to restart on the last level
        you died on. Or try "ROBOCOPPETER"

        Press the right mouse button during loading to see an advertisement
        for Robocop.

        On the title screen, type (with the 'CAPS LOCK' on) "MAGENTA", then
        during play press 'S' to open gate to the next level.

        After the title screen rolls around type "DAILY-88" for unlimited
        continues, do it with 'CAPS LOCK' on, also try "DALEY-88" or even
        "DALEY"

        Try typing "petejohnsonwantscheat" on the title screen.  Now
        pressing S in-game will open the exits.
